{"tid":1223620,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【國歌法】警察衝埋嚟嘅時候高唱義勇軍進行曲...","createTime":"2019-06-14T17:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T08:57:58.000Z","uid":196839,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"27353bdbbe68a56bfb66600c0616496dcb74f2bf","tid":1223620,"uid":196839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:58:07.000Z","msg":"雖然而家國歌法未有本地立法，但如果被傳媒影到香港警察暴力驅散一班身披五星紅旗、高唱國歌、喺公共場合學習「國歌的歷史和精神內涵」嘅<strong>愛國學生</strong>... 習近平睇到會點諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n－<br />\n<br />\n「奏唱國歌時，在場人員應當肅立，舉止莊重，不得有不尊重國歌的行為。」－《中華人民共和國國歌法》第七條<br />\n<br />\n「中小學應當將國歌作為愛國主義教育的重要內容，組織學生學唱國歌，教育學生了解國歌的歷史和精神內涵、遵守國歌奏唱禮儀。」－第十一條 <br />\n<br />\n「在公共場合,故意篡改國歌歌詞、曲譜，以歪曲、貶損方式奏唱國歌，或者以其他方式侮辱國歌的，由公安機關處以警告或者十五日以下拘留；構成犯罪的，依法追究刑事責任。」－第十五條"},{"pid":"31ad491e64eb599e1d548545f8288747350aecc1","tid":1223620,"uid":54904,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"好易比親中派造文章話全部遊行人士支持中國及修例"},{"pid":"9c6bd8fd57b47d18992f61a60ad70eb5520dee20","tid":1223620,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"31ad491e64eb599e1d548545f8288747350aecc1","tid":1223620,"uid":54904,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:01:40.000Z","msg":"好易比親中派造文章話全部遊行人士支持中國及修例"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:02:47.000Z","msg":"推 樓主請勿膠化"},{"pid":"38f7c8d0b337e10439b413621c25341e233b3f71","tid":1223620,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:03:43.000Z","msg":"我帶你還遊世界"},{"pid":"f2c6d2242f41201d5fec94d9962662338cf3eb1a","tid":1223620,"uid":230537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:16:54.000Z","msg":"好似行得通"},{"pid":"39e1ad3c01f65f5ff6f8dc9d7458b968a99c17ac","tid":1223620,"uid":130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:23:41.000Z","msg":"唔好膠啦。兒登。<br />\n<br />\n啲狗癲嫁。佢會停？<br />\n佢唔停，你寄望事後會入到佢罪？<br />\n剩係話咩執行緊職務，防止罪案發生，都有排佢up...<br />\n再講，人地打你，你唔走人，反以去唱歌？打到你唱唔到都仲得。"},{"pid":"3c928910e6b3cd7ad64830e2ad3c955e9c1fbfbf","tid":1223620,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2c6d2242f41201d5fec94d9962662338cf3eb1a","tid":1223620,"uid":230537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T18:16:54.000Z","msg":"好似行得通"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a7a58ee69fd6dfc45ff49182e2cfda15f64f11","tid":1223620,"uid":37537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:38:55.000Z","msg":"但其實明明國歌係革命歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99fa3066cdf68bcfaae5d0ac462d444b59057b6d","tid":1223620,"uid":196839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:57:48.000Z","msg":"愛國愛港，落實一國兩制，實行雙普選"},{"pid":"ecab37a570e408cda8d3edb8434fbe7ef747f1d1","tid":1223620,"uid":196839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:57:58.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"}]}